laboratory_examinations.findings: BACTEROIDES FRAGILIS GROUP, MIXED BACTERIAL FLORA (1.1, reference range 0.9 - 1.1)

Mild bibasilar atelectasis. No pleural or pericardial effusion. Multiple appendicoliths at the base of the appendix with fluid collection in the right lower quadrant suggesting rupture, measuring 3.1 x 3.2 x 4.8 cm. Associated inflammatory fat stranding and small free fluid. Terminal ileum is thickened. Small volume ascites. Remaining portions of small and large bowel are unremarkable.
